headline: Associated Bank Advances Credit Risk Strategy with Upgrade to FICO Auto Score 10
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., October 15, 2025--Associated Bank upgraded to FICO Auto Score 10, improving credit risk assessment and loan approval rates with better borrower predictions.
